data.description: Welcome to Bonanza Drive located in Richlands, where suburban living meets the tranquility of a half-acre lot without the hassle of an HOA. Nestled in a peaceful cul-de-sac, this two-story, 4-bedroom residence offers the perfect blend of convenience and spaciousness. Additionally with plenty of space outdoors, you will be able to bring your outdoor haven to life with this blank canvas. Contact me today to schedule a tour of this home and to take the next steps in making this exceptional property your own!
